{"tid":1668258,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"清算師全面進場 - 新戰線","createTime":"2019-10-22T01:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T04:04:01.000Z","uid":63100,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1fe85ef211f006a6f87ec030a84d28741f700149","tid":1668258,"uid":63100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:45:22.000Z","msg":"話說近排好多鋪頭裝修，<br />\n但係塊圍板又圍到出曬界，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條路窄左，行得唔舒服，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為小氣清算師嘅我，<br />\n緊係即刻睇下政府有無法例規管<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果我發現，原來根據土地（雜項條文）條例<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap28&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSMhAN7np5IU55thb9t6%2Bojg%3D&h=3bd2827f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap28</a><br />\n佔用政府未批租土地係要申請嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單d講，條街係政府地<br />\n如果佢地個圍板出左界又無申請<br />\n政府好似有權叫佢拆左佢嫁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家千祈唔好去地政總署問佢地有無申請呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係地政總署會比個deadline叫佢拆<br />\n佢都唔拆會再罰款同坐監嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加影，如果塊板搞到條路太窄<br />\n都可以打去屋宇署投訴嫁<br />\n行人路淨闊有都規例嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pland.gov.hk/pland_tc/tech_doc/hkpsg/full/pdf/ch8.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2